# Technology Stack Requirements

- Python 3.10+
- Dependency management: mamba / conda
- Code formatting: Ruff
- Type hinting: typing module (strict)
- Testing: pytest
- Documentation: Google style docstring
- Environment: conda / venv
- Containerization: docker, docker-compose
- Async: async/await
- Web: webrtc
- Demo: gradio, streamlit
- LLM: langchain, transformers
- Vector DB: faiss, chroma (optional)
- Experiment tracking: mlflow, tensorboard (optional)
- HPO: optuna, hyperopt (optional)
- Data: pandas, numpy, dask (optional), pyspark (optional)
- Version control: git
- Process: systemd, supervisor
